casebody.data:
Lorenzo OSBORNE
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided February 7, 2017

James E. Mortimer, assigned counsel, in support of the petition.

Adam E. Mattei, assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Lorenzo Osborne's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 170 Conn. App. 903, 152 A.3d 579 (2017), is denied.
